  codename: "Weight Space Scan — LLM Weight Introspection"

summary: |
  A proposed mechanism to read the `.gguf` weight blobs directly from disk and 
  compute their Shannon entropy. The original intent was to distinguish between 
  an RLHF-lobotomized model and an unfiltered base model by measuring distortion 
  signals within the weight matrices.

